敦伊丽莎白女王大厅大厅表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484609" class="wp-caption-text">斯凯·费雷拉 (Sky Ferreira) 于 2022 年 6 月 16 日在英国伦敦伊丽莎白女王大厅大厅表演。图片来源：洛恩·汤姆森/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>继 2013 年的《Night Time, My Time》之后的《Masochism》目前尚未确定正式上映日期。</p><p> Ferreira 于 2022 年 5 月带着<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sky-ferreiras-first-new-song-in-over-three-years-dont-forget-3233906">《Don&#39;t Forget》</a>回归，这是她自 2019 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/sky-ferreira-downhill-lullaby-masochism-track-review-2467684">《Downhill Lullaby》</a>以来的第一首歌曲。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-responds-to-billboard-claims-of-being-held-hostage-by-label-3484571">据报道，上个月，粉丝们在时代广场买了一个广告牌，展示费雷拉的照片，上面写着“Free Sky Ferreira”</a> ，声称她的音乐已被她的唱片公司 Capitol Records“扣押”了“近十年”。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-fly-free-sky-ferreira-banner-over-capitol-records-in-latest-protest-3502947">有人发现一架挂有同样呼吁的横幅的飞机飞过该品牌位于加利福尼亚州洛杉矶的总部上空</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-announces-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3503862">Sky Ferreira 宣布 2024 年英国和爱尔兰巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
基思·理查兹说新的清洁生活方式是“独特的体验” https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-says-new-clean-lifestyle-is-a-unique-experience-3503856?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=keith-richards-says-new-清洁的生活方式是一种独特的体验Max PilleyMon, 25 Sep 2023 16:01:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3503856 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="基思·理查兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我仍然喜欢偶尔喝一杯——因为我不会很快去天堂”</p><p>基思·理查兹<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-says-new-clean-lifestyle-is-a-unique-experience-3503856">(Keith Richards) 表示，新的清洁生活方式是“一种独特的体验”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="基思·理查兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/keith_richards_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/keith-richards">基思·理查兹 (Keith Richards)</a>表示，新的清洁生活方式对他来说是“一次独特的体验”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-rolling-stones-new-album-release-date-hackney-diamonds-3494545">滚石乐队的回归带来了更大的冲击</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/artists/keith-richards-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-interview/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《每日电讯报》</i></a>采访时，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>吉他手表示，自从戒毒和戒烟后，他正在“尝试享受异性恋”。</p><p> “我在 2019 年戒掉了香烟，”理查兹解释道。 “从那以后我就再也没碰过它们。我于 1978 年戒掉了海洛因。我于 2006 年戒掉了可卡因。</p><p> “我仍然喜欢偶尔喝一杯——因为我不会很快去天堂——但除此之外，我正在努力享受异性恋。这对我来说是一次独特的经历。”</p><p>这位 79 岁的老人还谈到了衰老过程，他说：“也许我很幸运，身体上的这种情况一直在持续。到目前为止，我对变老没有任何真正的问题。未来你可能会看到一些可怕的事情，但你必须到达那里。</p><p> “我已经接受了这样的想法：80 岁了，仍然走路，仍然说话。我发现[衰老]是一个令人着迷的过程。但如果你不这样做，你还不如自杀。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="滚石乐队 - 愤怒（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_mEC54eTuGw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-confirm-new-album-hackney-diamonds-and-single-angry-3494112">滚石乐队宣布了他们即将发行的第 24 张录音室专辑“Hackney Diamonds”的详细信息</a>。该专辑将于 10 月 20 日发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-hackney-diamonds-features-paul-mccartney-lady-gaga-elton-john-and-stevie-wonder-3498112">保罗·麦卡特尼、Lady Gaga、埃尔顿·约翰和史蒂维·旺德将参与其中</a>。</p><p>该专辑的主打单曲《Angry》现已上线，音乐视频由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/euphoria"><em>《Euphoria》</em></a>明星悉尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 主演。这将是滚石乐队自 2005 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-rolling-stones-7763-312997">《A Bigger Bang》</a>以来第一张原创专辑，也是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-drummer-charlie-watts-dies-aged-80-3027713">该乐队鼓手 Charlie Watts 于 2021 年去世</a>以来的第一张专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-reveal-charlie-watts-appears-on-two-tracks-of-new-album-hackney-diamonds-3494170">瓦茨的演奏将出现在两首新歌</a>《Mess It Up》和《Live By The Sword》中，后者也有滚石乐队创始人贝斯手比尔·怀曼的贡献。</p><p>乐队还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-working-on-new-documentary-about-making-of-hackney-diamonds-3499529">将制作一部与“Hackney Diamonds”相关的纪录片</a>，由<em>《卡戴珊姐妹》</em>的制作团队 Fulwell 73 制作。一位接近该项目的消息人士表示，这部电影将“让粉丝们亲密而坦诚地了解米克·贾格尔、基思和罗尼·伍德在工作室里施展魔法的过程，包括他们之间的玩笑。”</p><p>除了阐明他与毒品和酒精的关系外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-says-pop-music-has-always-been-rubbish-thats-the-point-of-it-3503510">理查兹还讨论了他对现代流行音乐的看法</a>，他说：“我不想开始抱怨流行音乐，它一直都是垃圾。我的意思是，这就是重点。”</p><p>当被问及他是否是嘻哈音乐迷时，他说：“我真的不喜欢听到人们对我大喊大叫并告诉我这是音乐，又名说唱。我不用离开家就可以受够了。”</p><p>基思·理查兹<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keith-richards-says-new-clean-lifestyle-is-a-unique-experience-3503856">(Keith Richards) 表示，新的清洁生活方式是“一种独特的体验”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
马丁·斯科塞斯希望你“反击”漫画电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/martin-scorsese-wants-you-to-fight-back-against-comic-book-films-3503854?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=martin-scorsese-wants-你反击漫画电影Adam StarkeyMon, 25 Sep 2023 15:51:06 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvel Cinematic Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3503854 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马丁斯科塞斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们必须拯救电影院”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/martin-scorsese-wants-you-to-fight-back-against-comic-book-films-3503854">马丁·斯科塞斯希望你“反击”漫画电影的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马丁斯科塞斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Martin-Scorsese-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>讨论了漫画电影和特许经营权对电影文化的影响，鼓励电影制片人和观众“反击”它。</p><p> The director, who <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/martin-scorsese-claims-marvel-movies-not-cinema-2554040">previously described Marvel movies as “not cinema” in the past</a> , tackled the topic once again during an extensive interview with <a href="https://www.gq.com/story/martin-scorsese-profile" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>GQ</em></a> .</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">&#39;Killers Of The Flower Moon&#39; review: Martin Scorsese&#39;s heartbreaking true crime chiller</a></strong></li></ul><p> “The danger there is what it&#39;s doing to our culture,” Scorsese said about the glut of comic book movies in cinemas. “Because there are going to be generations now that think movies are only those – that&#39;s what movies are.”</p><p> When the interviewer proposed many people already think that way, Scorsese agreed, adding: “They already think that. Which means that we have to then fight back stronger. And it&#39;s got to come from the grassroots level. </p><figure id="attachment_3448535" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3448535" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3448535" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon.jpg" alt="Killers Of The Flower Moon" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers_Of_The_Flower_Moon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3448535" class="wp-caption-text"> Robert De Niro and Leonardo DiCaprio in &#39;Killers Of The Flower Moon&#39;. CREDIT: Apple TV+</figcaption></figure><p> “It&#39;s gotta come from the filmmakers themselves. And you&#39;ll have, you know, the Safdie brothers, and you&#39;ll have <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">Chris Nolan</a> , you know what I mean? And hit &#39;em from all sides. Hit &#39;em from all sides, and don&#39;t give up. Let&#39;s see what you got. Go out there and do it. Go reinvent. Don&#39;t complain about it. But it&#39;s true, because we&#39;ve got to save cinema.”</p><p> The director said “manufactured content isn&#39;t really cinema”, adding: “It&#39;s almost like AI making a film. And that doesn&#39;t mean that you don&#39;t have incredible directors and special effects people doing beautiful artwork. But what does it mean? What do these films, what will it give you? Aside from a kind of consummation of something and then eliminating it from your mind, your whole body, you know? So what is it giving you?”</p><p> Scorsese&#39;s next film, <em>Killers Of The Flower Moon</em> , reunites the director with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">Leonardo DiCaprio</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-de-niro">Robert De Niro</a> . The film is centred on a series of Oklahoma murders in the Osage Nation in the 1920s, after oil was discovered on tribal land.</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">五星级评论</a>中将其描述为“一部将长期留在观众心中的电影”。</p><p> <em>Killers Of The Flower Moon</em> is set for release in cinemas from October 20, before it arrives on Apple TV+ at a later date.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/martin-scorsese-wants-you-to-fight-back-against-comic-book-films-3503854">Martin Scorsese wants you to “fight back” against comic book films</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
